comments: Grant (POR) moves alongside Davis' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the post shot attempt.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Reddish's (LAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Prince (LAL) lightly brushes Mays' (POR) arm and marginal contact occurs prior to release of his pass attempt.
Hachimura (LAL) moves toward Grant (POR) during his closeout and maintains legal guarding position contesting his jump shot attempt.
Mays (POR) places his hands against Hachimura's (LAL) body during his shooting motion and slides his hands off as marginal contact occurs during his layup attempt.
Prince (LAL) briefly places his hand against Mays' (POR) shoulder and slides his hand off, while defending over the pick.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Prince's (LAL) path and is firming up as marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Mays' (POR) path and marginal contact occurs to Mays' side as they disengage.
While contesting the driving shot attempt, Ayton (POR) makes contact with the ball and makes marginal contact with Reaves' (LAL) arm after the release.
Reaves (LAL) extends his arm outward and briefly grasps Ayton's (POR) arm during the release of his jump shot attempt.
Sharpe (POR) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Davis (LAL) after the release.
While defending the back cut, Reaves (LAL) makes marginal contact to Mays' (POR) arm on the play.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Camara (POR) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly given to LAL.
Sharpe (POR) briefly places his arm against Reddish's (LAL) hip before correcting.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Mays' (POR) path and is firming up as contact occurs.
Reaves (LAL) moves alongside Grant's (POR) path and absorbs the marginal body contact contesting Grant's driving shot attempt. While reaching down, he makes contact with the ball.
Mays (POR) commits a take foul on Hachimura (LAL).
Camara (POR) makes marginal contact with Reaves' (LAL) in transition.
Sharpe (POR) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
